  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/a078177aa19e914ae418f89c82338418.poster.avif?t=1684087457\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/a078177aa19e914ae418f89c82338418.webm?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/a078177aa19e914ae418f89c82338418.mp4?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Master the art of zero gravity warfare in Crossfar! Fight as a pilot, lead as a captain, and conquer as a general in intense PVP battles to earn your wings. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/7eda3fcd41af53237777e39afb85a5c8.poster.avif?t=1684087457\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/7eda3fcd41af53237777e39afb85a5c8.webm?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/7eda3fcd41af53237777e39afb85a5c8.mp4?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Perform spectacular maneuvers while free-floating and flying, as you zero down your aim to land your next shot center mass and reshape the frontlines of the galaxy! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/8bada2b00092870511ccd92ebf0256cf.poster.avif?t=1684087457\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/8bada2b00092870511ccd92ebf0256cf.webm?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/8bada2b00092870511ccd92ebf0256cf.mp4?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Prepare for tactical decision-making and explosive reactions at any moment! Work in a formation with your squad and utilize each drone's special abilities to gain supremacy over the battlefield. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/5eccb11c52eec9b8319ca30d9187222f.poster.avif?t=1684087457\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/5eccb11c52eec9b8319ca30d9187222f.webm?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/5eccb11c52eec9b8319ca30d9187222f.mp4?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Disarm, disable, distract or destroy enemy pilots to sneak past and breach their gate. Lure your enemies into a trap to counter their offensive or keep them at bay with sheer firepower! It's up to you and your team how you address every situation!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/7e06a4d571d8dc9545c7bf179170d433.poster.avif?t=1684087457\" width=624 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/7e06a4d571d8dc9545c7bf179170d433.webm?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2067300/extras/7e06a4d571d8dc9545c7bf179170d433.mp4?t=1684087457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>Grab your best squadron and join the competitive community in season tournaments, or watch the best professional teams battle it out in CROSSFAR LEAGUE!",
